 &lt;/figure>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>点击⚙，选择刚才新增的 Macro 名称然后叉掉即可；&lt;br>
&lt;figure>&lt;a class="lightgallery" href="https://bulone.github.io/posts/pougfvs/images/index-1742863657263.webp" title="如图" data-thumbnail="/posts/pougfvs/images/index-1742863657263.webp" data-sub-html="&lt;h2>如图所示&lt;/h2>&lt;p>如图&lt;/p>">&lt;img loading="lazy" src='https://bulone.github.io/posts/pougfvs/images/index-1742863657263.webp' alt="如图所示" height="402" width="989">&lt;/a>&lt;figcaption class="image-caption">如图&lt;/figcaption>
 &lt;/figure>&lt;/li>
